Chef Linda: This inviting stew is a study in taste, ease, and satisfaction. Simple ingredients dispel
the myth that vegan cooking is expensive and uses hard-to-find ingredients. The power in creating
plant-based food comes not only from what we leave out, but also what we include. Fresh ginger and
warming spices transform everyday sweet potatoes and ordinary peanut butter into a meal you’ll
hunger for again, before you even set your spoon down. Compassionate. Magical. Healthy. It’s one of
our favorites.
