techniques, ingredients, or nutritional concerns. This flavorful stew was created for a class on plantbased iron and calcium sources. Aside from being incredibly delicious and quick to assemble, it is a
nutritional powerhouse. Iron-rich cannellini beans mingle with calcium-rich collard greens, while the
