Preheat oven to 375°F. Line a baking tray with parchment. Brush oil
on the parchment.
Place beets, carrots, onion, mushrooms, and garlic in the bowl of a
food processor. Pulse until finely chopped. Empty into a large bowl.
Next, place oats, walnuts, chili powder, paprika, cumin, and salt into
