To Serve
1.
2.
Fresh salad greens, dressed in oil and lemon juice
Buns, with sliced tomato and avocado
1 batch Avocado-Scallion Sauce (pg. 185)
Directions
Preheat oven to 375°F. Line a baking tray with parchment. To make
burgers, pulse garlic in the food processor until finely chopped. Add
walnuts, flaxseed, hemp seeds, and pumpkin seeds. Pulse again until
finely chopped. Add vinegar, oil, tamari, and nutritional yeast, and
pulse again until blended. The mixture should be moist and hold
