Chef Sara: Packed with immunity-boosting ingredients, this savory broth is nothing short of
magical. Sip it straight up as a light and savory tea that’s a great home remedy for a cold, or serve
over rice noodles, fresh greens, and roasted tempeh for a full, yet light, meal.
