Directions
Preheat the oven to 375°F. Bring a large pot of salted water to a boil.
Add the ziti to the pot and cook according to package directions. With
about 5 minutes left to cook, add the cauliflower, and bring to a gentle
boil again. Continue cooking until pasta is al dente (soft with a little
bite to it) and cauliflower is fork-tender. Note that the addition of
