Preheat the oven to 375°F. Line two baking trays with parchment and
set aside.
In a small bowl, whisk together the flaxseed with the water to make a
“flax egg.” Set aside to thicken for about 5 minutes.
In a large bowl, whisk together the melted coconut oil, brown sugar,
maple syrup, and vanilla. Add the “flax egg” and whisk again until the
