Crust
1½ cups old-fashioned oats
¾ cup pecans
¼ cup coconut oil, melted
3 Tbsps maple syrup
¼ tsp salt
Custard
1 (13.5-ounce) can full-fat coconut milk
¾ cup plain nondairy milk
