volunteering at the Sanctuary on their winter break to create a teaching moment about the tragic lives
of dairy cows and egg-laying hens. Thankfully, everyone else who’s enjoyed this cake over the years
now knows that we can create our favorite foods without harming animals. This is a cake to savor:
